{"tid":2016774,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔知有冇人記得我地呢?]UP圖網 - image.cx","createTime":"2020-05-14T15:46:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T06:10:41.000Z","uid":45332,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"fc14e543262e78613342f6fc693e949086d376f0","tid":2016774,"uid":45332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T15:46:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.cx/content/images/system/logo_1588523962470_fcb804.svg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.cx%2Fcontent%2Fimages%2Fsystem%2Flogo_1588523962470_fcb804.svg&h=f89c0b4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔經唔覺，<br />\n<a href=\"http://image.cx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.cx&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7qDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=908da4f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">image.cx</a> UP圖網已經4年啦<br />\n捱到4年都重未收檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢可以一次upload多張圖片 <br />\n同時比哂咁多個IMG code比你 <br />\n又有相簿功能，剔返D相 <br />\n唔洗逐個CODE慢慢COPY<br />\n方便出POST放J圖既巴打 <br />\nBAM圖都OK <br />\n但係記得要SET做Private <br />\n每張圖最大50MB<br />\n歡迎各位巴絲開POST UP圖上黎<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://image.cx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.cx&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7qDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=908da4f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">image.cx</a>嘅<span style=\"color: orange;\">Chrome plugin</span>已經推出左啦，<br />\n啱哂經常偷圖珍藏嘅巴打，right click幅圖，Upload to <a href=\"http://image.cx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.cx&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7qDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=908da4f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">image.cx</a><br />\n就偷左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同時，我地好開心咁宣佈<br />\nGoogle Adsense重新批左廣告比我地啦<br />\n但我地嘅廣告收入一個月只係夠食半餐金拱門<br />\n遠低於SERVER嘅開支<br />\n<a href=\"http://希望大家加image.cx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6%E5%8A%A0image.cx&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7qDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=18b4fcae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">希望大家加image.cx</a>入你adblock嘅白名單<br />\n同時，<a href=\"http://有能力既巴打可以贊助image.cx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%9C%89%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B%E6%97%A2%E5%B7%B4%E6%89%93%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E8%B4%8A%E5%8A%A9image.cx&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7qDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=4664c447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">有能力既巴打可以贊助image.cx</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://image.cx/page/donate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.cx%2Fpage%2Fdonate&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7qDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=6b40bf41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://image.cx/page/donate</a> <br />\n五蚊十蚊都對網站有唔小既支持架 <br />\n<br />\n本站強制用HTTPS <br />\n同時本站支援IPV6 <br />\n不過係香港家用上網市場<br />\n應該得PCCW用到 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://image.cx/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.cx%2F&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7qDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=a162cc57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://image.cx/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n/-------------------同場推介-------------------/<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">BNO續領資訊</span> <br />\n唔洗比 9 假期老點，<br />\n睇住我地嘅Guidance 黎續BNO 就啱啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bnohk.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bnohk.org%2F&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7qDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=1a0dfb69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bnohk.org/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">檔案分享服務</span> <br />\n- 免註冊 <br />\n- 分享最大100MB的檔案 <br />\n- 檔案係一個月後刪除 <br />\n- 可加密碼保護 <br />\n- 可設第一個人下載後即時刪除 <br />\n- 上下載高速唔洗等秒數倒數<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://share.image.cx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshare.image.cx&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7qDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=e5ad0bd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://share.image.cx</a>"},{"pid":"94ab6e0f417fa40f67d5a334415bd10535fd15dc","tid":2016774,"uid":45332,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"c